@node "To Do" "To Do"

                                     To Do
                                     =====

Here is a list of features I may add in the future.

- Support for Multi-Part decodings.
- Proper support for more than one decoding per file.
- Support for encoding.
- A parameter to override the default filename.
- Support for yEnc V2 (probably when the standard is finalised).


